   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "205.640", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "211.520", 
   "id": "s000060", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Die Wochenenden verbringen die Kinder ebenfalls im Wechsel bei beiden Elternteilen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "211.520", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "214.600", 
   "id": "s000061", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Vater und Mutter k\u00f6nnen in ihren Jobs bleiben. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "214.600", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "216.920", 
   "id": "s000062", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Vielleicht kommt es auch zu der Konstellation, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "216.920", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "218.120", 
   "id": "s000063", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass der Vater, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "218.120", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "221.440", 
   "id": "s000064", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "weil der Mutter vielleicht eine bessere Stelle angeboten wird, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "221.440", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "223.520", 
   "id": "s000065", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "zu etwas mehr als 50\u00a0Prozent, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "223.520", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "225.240", 
   "id": "s000066", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "vielleicht zu 60\u00a0Prozent, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "225.240", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "226.680", 
   "id": "s000067", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "die Betreuung \u00fcbernimmt. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "226.680", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "227.000", 
   "id": "s000068", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Sprich: "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "227.000", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "230.080", 
   "id": "s000069", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
