   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "236.080", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "239.160", 
   "id": "s000072", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "bestimmt sich anteilig nach dem Einkommen beider. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "239.160", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "242.760", 
   "id": "s000073", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Vater und Mutter pr\u00e4gen die Kinder gleicherma\u00dfen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "242.760", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "245.120", 
   "id": "s000074", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "sind im Alltag f\u00fcr sie da. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "245.120", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "246.280", 
   "id": "s000075", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Kurzum: "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "246.280", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "249.480", 
   "id": "s000076", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Vater und Mutter kontrollieren die ersten Hausaufgaben, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "249.480", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "251.960", 
   "id": "s000077", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "und beide gehen mal in den Zoo. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "251.960", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "253.600", 
   "id": "s000078", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Das ist gerechter, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "253.600", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "258.480", 
   "id": "s000079", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "im Regelfall f\u00fcr die Kinder das Beste und auch international anerkannt."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "258.480", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "259.920", 
   "id": "s000080", 
